    "com/Yanan-Wang-cs/ClonedPerson) USynthFace (Boutros et al. 2023a) has also been generated using DiscoFaceGAN in combination with other GANs for data augmentation.",
    "This data set presents just one image per identity, leaving the users the task of generating further images if necessary, e.g., by data augmentation.",
    "The full data set contains a total of 400K images.",
    "SFace (Boutros et al. 2022) has been generated by translating a real public data set through StyleGAN2-ADA, which is a style-based GAN (Style-GAN2) with adaptive discriminator augmentation (ADA) to increase the diversity of the training data set.",
    "The real data set used both for training and translation is CASIA-WebFace (Yi et al. 2014)."
